c: 10
v: 54
t: "Yaye ukuba umntu ngamnye owenze ububi ebengaba nabo bonke ubutyebi beli hlabathi aze afune ukuzisindisa kuAllâh ngokuzihlawulela ngabo (bebungazi kwamkelwa kuye) baya kuba lusizi ezintliziyweni zabo xa besibona isohlwayo, yaye baza kugwetywa ngobulungisa akukho bugwenxa buya kwenziwa kubo"